metadata.name: Dreamologism #0001
metadata.description:
Oh, there she is

She's an unconventional woman

The one who walks on water

She comes around when

I'm losing sight of me

Hand in hand with the clockwork girl, we're getting it right

Straight out the gate she's

Taking me into overtime.

I need her more than ever.

If I jump, then she will fly because she

Knows all the right numbers to call on me.

I wake up and it's like she always knows what I'm dreaming of.

I didn't really need anyone.

I just needed somebody like her.

Dreams meet AI
